values:
Dear Jessenia,
Here is your love horoscope
for Friday, December 12:

Right now you don't need anything heavy in the relationship department. In fact, it might be best to keep your next romance light and easy. Keep fantasies about marriage, kids and a home in the 'burbs to yourself. Live and love in the now.

oh how funny life is..  hahahah
i am definitely overdue for one of those girls' night/drinking binge/venting sessions...
it may have not been the most logical or noble of gameplans, but at least i had one going. why did you have to go and screw it all up?

i love how when it seems everything seems to be going good in life, something just smacks me in the face to remind me that there's no such thing as "coasting". thank you highland park police for supplying the reality check this time. appreciate the ticket, too :)
eh, whatever. im over it. what i cant get over is the fact that i cant let this thing with you go. why cant i just accept you and be done with it? i continue to search for a flaw everywhere and make something ridiculous seem sooooo big when i hit a dead end. i have to stop this. and now.

you know, its funny how in the two or three years i have known you guys, i never got a phone call or text from any of you unless her phone was dead, but now that im 21, i get one practically every weekend from you guys. i dont mind doing a favor once or twice, but im beginning to feel as if im just being used for convenience. at first i was all, yea its whatever, but thinking back, i NEVER acted this way around my older friends just for my own pleasure. i mean, i may have done it a few times, but it wasnt like that. never out of the blue and never so consistently. i have to admit, its pretty fucked up. just thought you should know...

i wish i wouldnt try to find a flaw on every good guy that comes my way, but then welcome the bad boy with open arms. 
why am i such a glutton for punishment?

its nice to be reminded sometimes that im not so bad...
:)

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your horoscope
for Saturday, March 29:

Work or school comes first for you and while it may temporarily hamper your family or romantic life, the consequences won't be long-lasting. Try to make sure that you're keeping everyone in the loop!

completely true. so dont be angry if im getting lost in my work, it doesnt mean i dont love those closest to me, or miss those i havent seen/spoken to in a while. im still here :)

Florida. amazing weather. amazing people. amazing birthday. i def needed this vacation from work and home but i somehow feel like im out of the loop now and im struggling to get back. as for my 21st birthday, it was absolutely amazing. no lines, no cover charge, free drinks. $100 bills. nuff said. just ask amanda if you wanna know more, shes heard it enough.. haha but seriously, i had a great time. my dad even remembered to call me this year, even though he was a day early. that man will NEVER remember my exact birthday. its just now that im back, i dont know, things feel weird. work is horrendous with people being fucking retarded. i also dont need you trying to make me feel stupid every chance you get. i understand the situation buddy, you dont need to be an ass about it. sorry for actually having feelings. and wtf @ tonight being full of complete randomness?!? first of all, i thought once you found out i was only 21, you'd def be peacin'. but instead you came back 3 more times to talk.. hmmm.. is older really the route i should have been goin all along? and secondly- way to come out of fucking nowhere and provide for a VERY entertaining night. maybe my driveway wasnt the best of place for us to be nostalgic, but it was fun nonetheless. lets do it again sometime. maybe the beach! hahah.. alright i think i summed it up as briefly as possible without leaving out some important information. so yea, night.. 
oh and i hate that ive either been drunk, tipsy or hung over the past four nights.. i hope this is just a phase.. : /

i realize that my smoking is causing harm to not only myself, but to others as well. people that matter most in my life (and people that matter not so much, but thats not the point). i originally had the goal to be done with this hideous habit by the time i was 25, but 4 more years of this seems still too long. after many failed attempts i think i should give it one final try. especially since i had a dream the other day that i was this old nasty woman smoking a cigarette with my cheeks sucked in and eveything. not a pretty picture. 
but not to sound like a complete procrastinator, im gonna wait until i come back from florida... theres no way ill survive all that drinking without a cigarette.

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your single's love horoscope
for Thursday, February 21:

*It can't be fun and games all the time* and it's time to get your chores and errands out of the way so you can enjoy the weekend. 

* i wish i could learn to accept this.

nothing good ever comes for me without other not so good things following.. my life has seriously sucked for the past week. 

i hate my job right now. i get named front desk supervisor only to be taken advantage of my management and disrespected by employees everyday since then.. now i have to go in on my day off just cuz they said so. 

i miss you. i know were both busy and we pretty much have opposite schedules again, but we seriously need to find a day to catch up on all this time we've missed.. i love how its only been like two weeks tops, but it feels like forever.

i dont understand why your not answering the phone for me, but its starting to get upsetting. im your family and theres no reason to avoid me. so stop. please.

i know you think its cute, but im too old for these stupid games. its either there or its not. no more mixed signals, no more eluding. just fucking spit it out or go home.

im sorry she's gone. really, i am. but at the same time, i feel that her death was imminent. we all knew it was coming. im happy she lived a long and happy life. the woman was 115 years old for christ sake. id have to say that my biggest regret would be only having one memory of that woman in my 20 years of life. rip abuela dominga.

I dont know which one of you posted this, but i couldnt agree more. i <3 you all and miss you!  :D

Ive been secretly wanting the giants to win it since i found out they were going to the superbowl. why that is, doesnt really matter. but i just remembered that my dick of an ex-boyfriend is the biggest giants fan out there so now i want them to lose. horribly. i want them to crash and burn with everyone laughing and ridiculing the damn team, especially Eli fuckin Manning. nothing personal to the team or their quarterback. i just want to know that, somewhere, jon is beyond depressed, crying even, cuz i know he would.. is that cruel of me? hahaha

it has been a long time since someone held my hand for no other reason than to just hold it.. you are too cute for words..
im being extremely girly, but whatever, he makes me smile :D

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your horoscope
for Monday, January 28:

Your winning smile is all you really need to get your way at work today, so make sure you've got your game face on when dealing with coworkers or anyone else who might have what you want or need.

that pretty much described my night at work tonight.. three guests seriously wrote my manager a letter about how amazing my service was and how my "warm smile" alone brightened up their long day..

Trite, i know, but i finally decided that today was goin to be the day that i get up off my ass and do things ive been meaning to do. only the first thing i meant to do was hook up my printer to my computer, but i cant do that cuz my MOM BOUGHT ME EVERYTHING UNDER THE SUN FOR THIS FLIPPIN COMPUTER BESIDES A USB CABLE TO CONNECT THE PRINTER TO IT. needless to say, after taking everthing out of the box, setting it all up, and spending about an hour tryin to find one in my house, i have two options. 1~ wait until my mother gets home with one, or 2~ go out and but one myself.. for anybody else it would be one of those, "eh, its whatever" things, but im retarded. i refuse to wait until 630 to get a cable, but i dont feel like spending money on one. i just dont understand how there isnt even one in this house. both my parents worked with computers for over 10 years, my mother STILL works with computers. she brings computers home to fix! how is there not one usb cable around here?

to make matters worse, im one of those anal retentive people and refuse to go on with my day until this one task is completed correctly. i had my whole itinerary planned for the day and now its shot cuz of this. i mean, i could probably still do everything i wanted to do, but it wouldnt seem as efficient cuz it would require trips to some places more than once, which would waste my gas... im so difficult.. i swear, im gonna make one lucky man miserable for the rest of his life.. hahahah

With the lack of nicotine in my life, i have been craving chocolate. i bought three packs of chocolate tonight and their almost all gone already... i guess that;s slightly healthier, right? diabetes takes longer to kill than lung cancer... oh and after spending ten dollars on vitamin water that, although taste good, are not my favorite, my sister decides to tell me that XXX vitamin water has been on sale all week. sale ends tomorrow.. THANK YOU JENNIFER.!!

i found out tonight why i have not been promoted yet and its probably the most ridiculous thing i have ever heard in my life. apparently i cannot officially become supervisor yet because i havent been withe the company for 6 months yet. ive been in the hotel business for almost a year, but the 5 months at Dolce dont count. at least i only have like 3 weeks left until im at that 6 month mark. but really, what does time have to do with anything? if im the most qualified, im the most qualified. it shouldnt matter that i havent been here that long. i know how to do my job well, or you wouldnt have thought of me for the position in the first place. i guess i should just shut my mouth and feel lucky that i have superiors that look out for me enough to wait until that six month mark to post the job, instead of just hiring someone else or whatever. i need to stop stressing over this though, cuz in all seriousness, my problems wont come til after i get that position. he'll probably leave. i dont think he would leave angry at me, but thats always a possibility im preparing myself for. and as for her... damn, i dont know. i mean, i dont think she would leave for the simple fact she get go anywhere else, but i dont see her adjusting to all this and just being ok with the idea of working under me. shes to proud for that. a part of me hopes she'll get that transfer she wants before i get promoted, so there will be less pressure and drama surrounding their decision. but then another part, the bitchier part, of me cant wait to be her boss. i would LOVE to be the one that drove her away. that finally got her where she belongs-back on the street. but i guess well see. only 19 more days until its being posted :)

So maybe you're not as intriguing as you once were, but you're still adorable. 
mhmm..

i guess ill be starting '08 single... gee, thanks : /

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your single's love horoscope
for Friday, January 4:

Even if your romantic prospects are as flat as New Year's champagne, you still have tons of other great opportunities. Pick up the phone today and make contact with family and old friends. You'll appreciate the chance to become reacquainted.

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your single's love horoscope
for Sunday, December 23:

Your reaction may be immediate and strong, but do you really want to put it out there as-is? Take a deep breath and let your thoughts and feelings evolve. Try bouncing it off a trusted friend.

As a "superior" shouldnt you be acting like the bigger person here? i dont care what kind of position i put you in, you should, and have to, accept my decision. being a complete ass about it isnt gonna change or make things better. so deal with it and grow the fuck up. 

thanks! :)

LOL @ possibilities flying from every possible direction EXCEPT THE ONE I WANT IT FROM!!!!
WTF LIFE? why you gotta play me like that?

damn.. i dont think i have ever been this nervous about talking to someone before..

>.<

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your single's love horoscope
for Saturday, October 13:

Don't be afraid to assert yourself today. If you want to know where you stand with a certain person, ask them. You're too effervescent and vivacious to let anyone undermine your confidence


on a different note, I NEED A HALLOWEEN COSTUME!!!
I GIVE UP ON AUTOMOBILES.. anybody wanna spend their time carting me around?
i wish you'd take this a little more seriously than you do
since when does being doubtful, mean your fucking smiling? i dont really know about you guys, but i do not tend to smile in that mood. maybe its time, these smileys get fixed or something, hmmm?

igotmycarback

igotmycarback

I GOT MY CAR BACK TODAY!!!! wootttt... sorry, im just uber excited that i can do pretty much anything now.. even sleep over his house without any inconveniences.. im just hoping he asks.
i am way too excited about tomorrow morning.  it seriously cant come soon enough

i dont quite know how to explain what it is you do to me. you inspire me to do things with myself. you make me want to be better than i am. and not by being the epitome of everything i dont wanna become, like others have. i can feel lost or pressured with so many things, but i talk to you for as little as five minutes and i already have a plan to work things out. i know what im gonna do with myself. and none of this comes from you telling me what to do.. i guess the best way to put it is you listen to me without fault. you listen to the point where i dont hold ANYTHING back, therefore, i dont have to think about these problems myself. i just release them and almost instantly all my problems are replaced by possible solutions or a new view of how retarded im being and how its not a problem at all and i can just let things go. you allow me to be happy. i dont worry so much when i get my fix. i hate to say it in those terms, but you are kinda like a drug to me.. when i know that im gonna be seeing you, my day seems that much better. i strive to see you and dread the days when i know you wont be there for me.. 

       i know this is a little selfish to say, but now that i know how much you mean to me, i want to mean that much to you. i want you to come to me with your daily dilemmas. i want you smile after telling me how terrible your day was because i managed to make it all go away. 

   i guess i just want something else to make us more connected than everyone else around here, yanno?
you have something to say, so say it. you know we both can handle that better than silence and tension..
i cannot believe the things that occurred last night were real... crazy night with crazy people and crazy alcohol. i <3 the people in my life right now and the good times we have together...

Is it wrong that im my happiest when im at work? it seems like the place where im supposed to have the most responsibility and be on my best behavior is turning into my safe haven from all that i need to escape.. what is going on in my life and why do i hate 11:15 coming EVERY night?

So who wants to join me in going tomorrow? i cant drive, but i'll pay.... its gonna be soooo beautiful out, like 85 and i REALLY REALLY wanna go before i go down to georgia cuz i dont know when i'll be able to go when i come back... can someone mae these dreams come true?

ok, so i just posted an entry that was a little harsh. i refuse to retract it however, because i do feel that way and i never want to speak to that girl again. there i no way what she did go fade away with an apology. i guess i just want it said that if something happens to the girl, its probably not me... its KARMA. shes not worth me wasting breath nor physical activity like a beating. but, karma will come around to her and for that, i warn you little girl because karma is not forgiving...

I found out today that there is a group of hollywood actors, 12% to be exact, that cannot be linked to Kevin Bacon. I have been playing this stupid fucking game trying to find one and i can't!  this game must rot in hell and Kevin Bacon must NEVER do another movie again.... ok, maybe like 2 or 3 more, but thats it Kevin, i mean it.
k. thanks!

NOT GAS! Because love never really runs out. there's always someone somewhere loving someone else. and im sure love isn't quite expensive. and im sure if your car runs out of love you dont need to wait for like 2 hours for AAA to put some more love in it.... yup. i've decided to make to first ever car that runs on love. EVERYBODY WHO IS ANYBODY is gonna want it.... just you wait and see



and grr... at AAA for being jerks. i called them and asked if there was any way for them t meet me at my car at 11:15 so i wouldnt have to wait for them for like 2 hours after i got out and the asshole receptionist said that tehy dont make emergency appointments. its either oneor the other... so now i have to wait til like 11:30 when i get out of here to call them THEN wait forever til they get here... UGH!!!

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your single's love horoscope
for Monday, June 25:

Try not to take it too personally now. A detached perspective lets you see the real extent of your role, and the role of timing and sheer randomness. A friend can help you evaluate honestly too. 


friend, help me evaluate, cuz idfk what the hell im doing!

Ok, so i know this is COMPLETELY random, but why am i always hungry? i'll eat until i'm full, and i never starve myself, but i always seem to be hungry about 45 minutes after i eat. its like my stomach is some sort of bottomless pit and there' not satisfying it.... ok, i'm done cuz now i'm getting even hungrier just thinking about food

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your horoscope
for Saturday, June 23:

A new admirer is being ridiculously sweet. Part of you doesn't trust this -- who do they think you are? Is it possible that they see exactly what it is you are -- someone who deserves lots of love?
Why do i make such stupid decisions?

So, im pretty sure i made this HUGE mistake last night, on more than one count, but im not really feeling too bad or guilty or anything. i mean, granted i regret one detail, but for the most part, it was fine. more than fine actually.. i mean, if i had the chance to redo last night, most of it would go the same way. im sorry i dont feel bad, M, i really am, but i cant force feelings that arent there...

June
This is a hot month for you in the romance department, so don't worry about a thing! Whether you are single or not, there are plenty of opportunities for love at your doorstep. Indeed, with your planetary ruler Mars raging through your sign for the first three weeks of June, you'll be on fire with sexual prowess. Your powers of attraction are unstoppable and everyone around you wants to get a step closer. Whatever you want you can have, so don't be afraid to go big. Opportunities that are present now may not be available next month. Make a move!


you hear that boys? start lining up, im ready for you... ;)

So this first one came a day late, but tell me this isn't completely accurate:

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your love horoscope
for Sunday, June 10:

They're gonna love you -- if you don't totally bowl them over. You've got some great energy now, and anyone who can keep up with you will absolutely adore it -- though a shy type might be overwhelmed! 

then there's this one:

Dear Jessenia,
Here is your love horoscope
for Monday, June 11:

The romantic energy may not be of the wild, passionate kind, but you've got a nice little vibe going. Start slow now and take a friends-first approach. Relax and enjoy yourself, and see what develops. 

I love it when i feel horoscopes were specifically written for me!

Ok, so i probably had like the best weekend ever... friday was a pretty rocky start but the trip to the city then nicole's beach house made my day. i had the most delicious burger and chocolate milkshake in this place you would never know existed unless you were taken there, which i was. then the impromptu trip to point pleasant was absolutely lovely. i don't think i've had that much fun in a while. and yesterday, dont even get me started on that. first off, bobby and i saved the night with a detour to south plainfield for some ahem refreshments. everybody was just so chill and amazing. oh, and i gave some poor ugly guy my "number"-actually just a combination of numbers that wont add up to anything... and to top the whole night off, i feel my bestest best friend in the whole wide world and i got even closer, and to tell you the truth, i didnt think it was possible and i realized once again how much i enjoy having a friend like her. scratch that, how lucky i am to have a friend like her. 


oh and yes, i did say some things i probably shouldn't have, but whats a fun drunk night without saying something that could get you in trouble.... and i know its off the wall and seems like it came out of nowhere, but it hasnt. thats been there for a while, ive just been trying to ignore it

lemme tell you how angry i am with this new company running the hotel...
1~ they change ownership in the middle of the week during the busiest month of the year.
2~ they do not have any properties in Georgia
3~the new gm is a big ----. the old one was WAY better, but then again, maybe im a little biased.
4~ biggest reason ever right here: they put some stupid software in the stupid computer that blocks stupid popups so now i cant go on aim anymore... STUPID DOLCE I HATE YOU!!!

I wanna go back to the old days. when we used to be forced to color, take naps, and have play/share time in kindergarten... i definitely wouldn't complain about any of this nearly as much as i used to... i always wanted to be a big girl when i was 5. now, im wishing i could just do it over and appreciate all the downtime and complex-free experiences.
